description: Try our easy to follow Wholemeal Pumpkin & Chocolate Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Chocolate cake,High fibre,Seafood free,Soy free,Tree nut free,Pumpkin,Sesame free,Baking,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Wholemeal Pumpkin & Chocolate Cake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 cup cocoa powder (save 1/2 cup for dusting)

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Grease a 22cm round cake tin and line base with baking paper.
Combine flour, cocoa powder, baking powder and pumpkin in a large bowl.
Whisk eggs with maple syrup, oil and vanilla extract. Add to dry ingredients and mix well.
Transfer to cake tin and smooth top. Bake for 4045 minutes or until firm to touch. Cool in tin for 5 minutes then turn out on a wire rack to cool.
Dust cake with extra cocoa powder and drizzle with extra maple syrup. Slice and serve.
